---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section section--tint is3-cards">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="is3-cards__heading">Choose Your Level of Immune Support</h2>

    <div class="is3-cards__grid">

      <!-- IMMUNITY Signature -->
      <div class="is3-cards__card">
        <h3 class="is3-cards__card-title">IMMUNITY Signature</h3>
        <p class="is3-cards__card-kicker">Best for proactive wellness and maintaining your baseline and as a pre-travel immune boost</p>
        <p class="is3-cards__card-body">This drip is packed with a powerful blend of essential vitamins and minerals to form the foundation of your immune health.</p>
        <ul class="is3-cards__list">
          <li>Vitamin C, B-Vitamins, &amp; Zinc: Work together to fuel immune cell function and fight off pathogens.</li>
          <li>Magnesium &amp; Minerals: Help reduce inflammation and support overall cellular health.</li>
          <li>Amino Acids &amp; Folic Acid: Provide the essential building blocks for a healthy system.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- IMMUNITY Deluxe -->
      <div class="is3-cards__card">
        <h3 class="is3-cards__card-title">IMMUNITY Deluxe</h3>
        <p class="is3-cards__card-kicker">Best for maximum defense when you need to recover from flu faster or are feeling run down. This is our most potent high-dose vitamin C IV formula.</p>
        <p class="is3-cards__card-body">Our Deluxe drip starts with the same powerful foundation as the Signature drip but adds a trio of high-potency ingredients to supercharge your recovery.</p>
        <p class="is3-cards__card-body">The key difference. This trio of high-potency ingredients is added to supercharge your recovery:</p>
        <ul class="is3-cards__list">
          <li>Glutathione: The body&#39;s &#39;master antioxidant.&#39; It neutralizes free radicals, supports liver detoxification, and helps your immune cells function at their peak.</li>
          <li>Taurine: An amino acid that protects your cells from stress and supports the healthy function of your immune and cardiovascular systems.</li>
          <li>Niacin (Vitamin B3): A powerful B-vitamin that improves circulation, supports cellular energy production, and has anti-inflammatory properties.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="is3-cards__cta">
      <a href={site.calcomUrl} class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .is3-cards__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .is3-cards__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .is3-cards__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .is3-cards__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .is3-cards__card-kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .is3-cards__card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .is3-cards__list {
    list-style: disc;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 0 0 1.2em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .is3-cards__list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .is3-cards__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .is3-cards__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .is3-cards__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
